Uses of Package
org.eng.aisp.feature

  • Packages that use org.eng.aisp.feature 
    Package Description
    org.eng.aisp
    The base package containing some of the core interfaces and classes.
    org.eng.aisp.classifier
    Defines a general framework for training on and classifying data streams.
    org.eng.aisp.classifier.anomaly  
    org.eng.aisp.classifier.anomaly.normal  
    org.eng.aisp.classifier.cnn  
    org.eng.aisp.classifier.dcase  
    org.eng.aisp.classifier.gaussianmixture
    Provides an implementation of a Gaussian Mixture Model-based classifier.
    org.eng.aisp.classifier.gmm  
    org.eng.aisp.classifier.knn
    Provides a framework for classifiers that use nearest neighbor distance metrics.
    org.eng.aisp.classifier.knn.merge
    Implements nearest neighbor algorithms that merge sub-features for training and classification.
    org.eng.aisp.classifier.mvi  
    org.eng.aisp.feature
    Defines a framework for features and the operations on them including extractiong and processing.
    org.eng.aisp.feature.extractor
    Defines IFeatureExtractor and support classes.
    org.eng.aisp.feature.extractor.vector
    Defines IFeatureExtractor implementations over vectors of double values.
    org.eng.aisp.feature.io
    Provides support for reading/writing features from/to the file system.
    org.eng.aisp.feature.pipeline
    Provides the class that defines the feature extraction process including sub-windowing, extraction and processing.
    org.eng.aisp.feature.processor
    Defines IFeatureProcessor, support classes and implementations.
    org.eng.aisp.feature.processor.vector
    Provides implementations of feature processors over vectors of double values.
    org.eng.aisp.tools
    Provides a set of command line tools for training, classifying, capturing, and storing sounds.
    org.eng.aisp.util
    Various utilities specific to the sound project code base.
